launcher.title: Seol teachtaireacht saincheaptha
launcher.description: Mar forbróir is féidir leat teachtaireachtaí a sheoladh chuig do chuid feidhmeanna.

infohub_trigger.YOU_AS_A_DEVELOPER_CAN_SEND_A_MESSAGE_TO: Is féidir leat mar forbróir teachtaireacht a sheoladh chuig do breiseán ag teacht chun cinn.
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_NODE_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE_MES: Roghnaigh an nód mian leat a sheoladh chuig an teachtaireacht a
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_PLUGIN_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE_M: Roghnaigh an breiseán mian leat a sheoladh chuig an teachtaireacht a
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_FUNCTION_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE: Roghnaigh an fheidhm is mian leat a sheoladh ar an teachtaireacht a
infohub_trigger.THIS_IS_THE_MESSAGE_YOU_CAN_SEND_TO_THE_: Is é seo an teachtaireacht is féidir leat a sheoladh chuig an breiseán roghnaithe.
infohub_trigger.THE_MESSAGE_YOU_SEE_IS_THE_DEFAULT_VALUE: Is é an teachtaireacht a fheiceann tú na luachanna réamhshocraithe an fheidhm atá leagtha.
infohub_trigger.HERE_YOU_WILL_SEE_THE_RESPONSE_FROM_THE_: Anseo feicfidh tú an freagra ón fheidhm.
